{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3ec66941f6","title":"烧黄公略联","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b7c7876068","index":0,"year":1931,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"3ec66941f6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji5","name":"毛泽东全集第5卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji5.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"efe954eb4c","type":"paragraph","text":"烧黄公略联","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji5","articleId":"3ec66941f6"},{"id":"c2fe784bf0","type":"paragraph","text":"（1931年9月）广州暴动不死，平江暴动不死，而今党辆性，进根大锅从天落革命战争有功，游击战争有功，毕生何奋男，好教后世继君来[1]1931年9月15日，部队在转移中，黄公路率红三军开赴瑞金，途经江西吉安东固六减四山峡，突遇敌机扫射。他一面组织队伍隐蔽疏散，一面指挥对空射击，不幸中弹晒鞋，插性时年仅三十三岁。9月16日下午，红军在兴国莲村举行追峰大会，毛泽东素自主持了大会，并亲笔写下这副钱联挂于会场主席台两旁。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji5","articleId":"3ec66941f6"}],"page":{"id":"108be50531","publicationId":"maoquanji5","articleId":"3ec66941f6","start":394,"end":394}}}},"__N_SSG":true}